QuestData.Title: Spiral Yeti Horn
QuestData.Description:
All manner of creatures are attracted to the sweet smell of fresh honey, but relatively few are willing to withstand the painful and often deadly stings of the largest of bees. This yeti, however, has been a persistent thorn in the hive's side, until now.
The Hivemother will be interested in this item.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Spiral Yeti Horn to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Take the Spiral Yeti Horn to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
